title: Xyron Permanent Adhesive Refill for Create-a-Sticker XRN500, 5" x 20', Refill Cartridge (AT1505-20)
description: The Xyron 5" Create-A-Sticker Permanent Refill cartridge is 20' long and fits into a Xyron 5” Create-A-Sticker. Enjoy making permanent stickers from items up to 5" wide. It's great for photos, cards and more.
